Step 1- Open terminal, and type the following lines.

            sudo add-apt-repository ppa:hanipouspilot/rtlwifi
            sudo apt-get update
            sudo apt-get install rtlwifi-new-dkms
            
Step 2- Reboot your system. If the problem persists, follow the next steps.
Step 3- Type the following line in the terminal in terminal, and hit enter. 

            echo "options rtl8723be ant_sel=2"  | sudo tee /etc/modprobe.d/rtl8723be.conf
            
        Now, reboot and enjoy.
        
